   LIFESTYLE/FEATURES (``l'' category)
</P>
<P>
   CHRISTIAN-DOCS (Nuevo Lardeo, Mexico) _ Dr. Ken Long is among
the doctors, dentists and other caregivers who cross the border
from the United States to provide health care to needy Mexicans.
The San Antonio Area Christian Medical and Dental Society sponsors
eight of these trips a year to northern Mexico border cities. By
SUZANNE HOHOLIK. (Photo available on Wieck database.)
</P>
