   SALTER-COLUMN (San Francisco) _ Reporting on the debacle in
Kosovo and Serbia, an radio correspondent said that diplomats were
working behind the scenes ``to find a resolution that will allow
both Mr. Milosevic and Mr. Clinton to save face.'' Save face? I
can't keep the faces of Milosevic and Clinton in focus, let alone
grasp the value of saving them. By STEPHANIE SALTER.
