   VIDEO-LONGINO _ Only one thing can come of Hollywood's recent
teen movie glut: a teen video glut. Several less-than-stellar
depictions of American teen life _ like ``Varsity Blues'' _ are
headed for the video stores in the coming weeks. So here are a
dozen alternatives for your kid, mostly older and better movies
depicting various aspects of teen life. Like ``American Graffiti,''
``Breaking Away,'' ``Native Son'' and, of course, ``Rebel Without a
Cause.'' (Longino, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
