<P>
   CHINA-TIANAMENN (Beijing) _ Developments as Friday's 10th
anniversary of Tianamenn massacre approaches: The People's Daily
makes unusual explicit mention of the crackdown, CNN ordered shut
off in hotels, several dissidents arrested. By Erik Eckholm.
</P>
<P>
   NKOREA-CHINA (Beijing) _ In a trip being watched closely by the
United States and Asia, North Korea's No. 2 official is coming to
Beijing for the first high-level visit in eight years. By Erik
Eckohlm.
