<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY &LR;  &QC; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; A PUNISHED CHINA COULD PROVE EVEN MORE DANGEROUS TO AMERICA &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (900 words) &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Moved as BC-I-SPY-GONE-AWRY-ECONOMIST-NYTSF &LR;  &QL; 
 &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; THE TRANSFORMATION OF POST-MANDELA SOUTH AFRICA &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (ATTN: Commentary Editors) &QL;
</P>
