<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BLAME-YOURSELF-YANKS-COX-ECONOMIST-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PEKING MUCK: HOW DID SO MANY PEOPLE LOOK THE WRONG WAY?  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors...NOTE 250-word trim at 675)   (This excellent ``separate buy'' article is from the current (week
beginning 29 May 1999) ECONOMIST magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
in Canada except to The Toronto Globe &AMP; Mail.)  
  
 (To publish this article, it must be purchased from the New York
