<P>
   NATO-EXERCISE (Vyskov, Czech Republic) _ Soldiers from 20 NATO
countries and allies are seeking to end a longstanding ethnic
conflict and create a buffer zone for refugees. But any resemblance
between the exercise and the conflict taking place two countries
away is purely coincidental, officials insist. By Rick Jervis. 700
words.
</P>
