</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   PUSHKIN-POEM _ ``Exegi Monumentum,'' one of his most famous
works.
</P>
<P>
   SAFRICA-RADIO _ South Africa's most prominent radio talk-show
host has a talent for getting other people to talk. By Kurt
Shillinger. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   GAY-FILM (Undated) _ A documentary to be aired on PBS that
raises issues about homosexuality in schools opens up a new front
in the battle between gay advocates and conservative religious
groups. By Diego Ribadeneira. 1200 words.
</P>
<P>
   HARVARD-REICH (Boston) _ Economic titans Alan Greenspan and
Robert Reich will deliver dueling commencement addresses next week.
By James Bandler. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY (k) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   NYHAN-COLUMN (Dingle, Ireland) -- With tourists and hard
