sister of James Williams, who was tried four times for the shooting
death of a young man named Danny Hansford, which was the focus of
the bestseller ``Midnight in the Garden of Good and Evil.'' If sold
at anywhere near that price, Mercer House would be the most
expensive private house _ by far _ ever sold in Savannah. By Tracie
Rozhon.
