   THOMPSON-COLUMN (Washington) _ Out of the consternation and
confusion over the House report on Chinese spying in the United
States, one fact emerges: Rep. Christopher Cox is not Joe McCarthy.
Cox, a thoughtful California conservative, has made no attempt to
exploit for domestic political gain his committee's findings that
China stole U.S. nuclear secrets. By ROBERT E. THOMPSON.
