<HEADER>
A0069 &Cx1f; tad-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-JOURNAL-IRAQ-0603-COX     06-02 0830
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-JOURNAL-IRAQ-0603-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    FREEDOM IN KURDISTAN ILLUSTRATES REPRESSION IN IRAQ
 &HT;    With Photos; Photo mug of Kaplow.
 &HT;    EDs: For purposes of a locator map Kurdistan is in northeastern
Iraq; Erbil is in central Kurdistan and Suleimaniyah it to the
east.
 &HT;    Moving in both (i) International and (k) Commentary categories.
 &HT;    By LARRY KAPLOW 
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service 
<TEXT>
