<HEADLINE>
ONCE OBSCURE, ARGENTINE COMPOSER IS NOW OMNIPRESENT
</HEADLINE>
 
EDS: Restores missing first reference to conductor German
Gutierrez (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By WAYNE LEE GAY 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   Ten years ago, most of us had never heard of Astor Piazzolla.
</P>
<P>
   Now, his music is everywhere. A classical guitar concert without
the music of Piazzolla is a rarity these days; Russian violinist
