<P>
   KOSOVO-PLANE (In Flight Over Kosovo) _ First-hand account of
reporter's ride on a NATO warplane during bombing mission over
Kosovo. By Michael R. Gordon.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-DIPLOMACY (Berlin) _ Russia and the West on Wednesday
narrowed their differences over the concrete measures required to
end the war in Kosovo, limiting the room for maneuver of Yugoslav
President Slobodan Milosevic and increasing the pressure on him to
reach a settlement. By Roger Cohen.
