   Kids: ``The Berenstain Bears,'' three new volumes, three
episodes per tape, $9.95 each. ``The Muppet Movie,'' ``The Great
Muppet Caper'' and ``The Muppet's Take Manhattan,'' $14.95 each.
</P>
<P>
   Crime caper: ``Out of Sight,'' VHS $14.98. DVD, $29.98.
</P>
