   BC-COMPUTERS-CYBERSPACE-BOS (Undated) _ Where do you go when
you're suffering brain cramps? You could stare at a wall, but you
feel like you need something a little bit more, well, artistic. The
Museum of Web Art is the perfect antidote, an on-line gallery that
is the visual equivalent of ambient music. By Patti Hartigan.
</P>
