<P>
   KOSOVO-DIPLOMACY (Berlin) _ Russia and the West narrow their
differences over the concrete measures required to end the war in
Kosovo, limiting the room for maneuver of Yugoslav President
Slobodan Milosevic and increasing the pressure on him to reach a
settlement. By Roger Cohen.
