   _  &UR; Jason Alexander &LR;  (not the actor) says a classified-ad taker
became cool on the phone when he dictated his description of
himself as an `` &UR; Ayn Rand &LR;  admirer missing heroine.'' He found out
why when the ad said he was ``missing heroin.''
