remember when she finds something amusing or pleasant: ``When
smiling, lift the corners of your lips but don't flash your teeth.
Quiet amusement gives your face an air of tranquil mystery.''
</P>
<P>
   _ Researchers at the University of Michigan ``were asked to
complete a math test while alone in a room and wearing either a
sweater or a bathing suit,'' reports Self magazine. ``All of the
women scored lower than the men, and the women in swimsuits did
worse than the women in clothes.'' The finding: Women's
self-consciousness ``interfered with their performance.''
</P>
