<P>
   &UR; READING BY GENDER &LR;
</P>
<P>
   Bitch, one of the new crop of tough-minded magazines for women,
analyzes the new crop of quasi-porn magazines for sex-minded men.
In a table comparing Arena, Bikini, Deluxe, Gear, Loaded, Maximum
and Stuff, the seven men's magazines have the following details in
common:
</P>
<P>
   _ They all have a woman wearing few clothes on the cover.
</P>
<P>
   _ They all include photos of men wearing neon-colored anoraks.
</P>
<P>
   _ They all contain computer-game reviews.
</P>
