<HEADLINE>
`PILONCILLO' LEAVES BITTER TASTE FOR SPELLING CONTESTANT 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 By MARK HELM  
 c.1999 Hearst Newspapers  
<TEXT>
<P>
   WASHINGTON _ Andrew Shawhan, a seventh-grader from Delmar, N.Y.,
