<SLUG> BC-QUOTE-OF-THE-DAY-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-PLANE-CRASH-NYT, which moved in
``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``When we came to a stop I looked over my shoulder and saw a
fireball coming down the aisle. I thought, `Forget the purse,
woman, get out of the plane.'''
</P>
<P>
   _PHYLLIS CARUTH, a passenger on the jet that slid off a runway
in Arkansas late Tuesday.
</P>
</TEXT>
