-- Aaron Copland in 1980. Plans for ``Copland 2000,'' a worldwide
celebration of theAaron Copland's music and contributions to
American culture were announced this week. Copland, who was born in
Brooklyn, would have turned 100 on Nov 14, 2000. He died in 1990.
(Paul Hosefros/New York Times Photo)
