   (NYT5) SACRAMENTO, Calif. -- June 2, 1999 -- FLA-CONNERLY, 6-2
-- Attorney Ward Connerly outside his office in 1997. Connerly, the
man who campaigned successfully to end affirmative action in
government hiring and school admissions in California and
Washington state, has now aimed his crusade at Florida, to the
sound of slamming doors. (Don Preisler/New York Times Photo)
