<DOCNO> NYT19990602.0513 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-06-02 23:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0969 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-THAILAND-HOTEL-NYT &LR;      06-02 0912
